item.title: Julie add a quote by Paulo Coelho
item.description: "There is only one thing that makes a dream impossible to achieve: the fear of failure." -- Paulo Coelho

item.title: Julie add a quote by Bob Ross
item.description: "We don't make mistakes, just happy little accidents." -- Bob Ross

item.title: Julie add a quote by Khalil Gibran
item.description: "Your joy is your sorrow unmasked. And the selfsame well from which your laughter rises was oftentimes filled with your tears. And how else can it be? The deeper that sorrow carves into your being, the more joy you can contain." -- Khalil Gibran

item.title: Julie add a quote by Kahlil Gibran
item.description: "You talk when you cease to be at peace with your thoughts." -- Kahlil Gibran

item.title: Julie add a quote by Maurice Switzer
item.description: "It is better to remain silent at the risk of being thought a fool, than to talk and remove all doubt of it." -- Maurice Switzer

item.title: Julie add a quote by Bernard M. Baruch
item.description: "Be who you are and say what you feel, because those who mind don't matter, and those who matter don't mind." -- Bernard M. Baruch

item.title: Julie add a quote by Confucius
item.description: "I hear and I forget. I see and I remember. I do and I understand." -- Confucius

item.title: Julie add a quote by Henry Ford
item.description: "Whether you think you can, or you think you can't--you're right." -- Henry Ford

item.title: Julie add a quote by Henry David Thoreau
item.description: "I learned this, at least, by my experiment: that if one advances confidently in the direction of his dreams, and endeavors to live the life which he has imagined, he will meet with a success unexpected in common hours." -- Henry David Thoreau

item.title: Julie add a quote by Kyle mIller
item.description: "You're not going to die in a rickshaw in Durham. " -- Kyle mIller

item.title: Julie add a quote by Elizabeth Gilbert
item.description: "God dwells within you, as you." -- Elizabeth Gilbert

item.title: Julie add a quote by Eudora Welty
item.description: "it doesn t matter if it takes a long time getting there; the point is to have a destination." -- Eudora Welty
